[
  {
    "startTime": 12.88,
    "endTime": 15.679,
    "text": "so i want to talk to you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.679,
    "endTime": 18.24,
    "text": "about the forgotten middle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.24,
    "endTime": 20.4,
    "text": "to me they're the students"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.4,
    "endTime": 21.76,
    "text": "co-workers"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.76,
    "endTime": 24.0,
    "text": "and plain old regular folks"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.0,
    "endTime": 26.08,
    "text": "who are often overlooked"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.08,
    "endTime": 27.599,
    "text": "because they're seen as neither"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.599,
    "endTime": 28.96,
    "text": "exceptional"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.96,
    "endTime": 31.119,
    "text": "nor problematic"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.119,
    "endTime": 34.079,
    "text": "they're the kids we think we can ignore"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.079,
    "endTime": 36.399,
    "text": "because their needs for support"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.399,
    "endTime": 39.36,
    "text": "don't seem particularly urgent"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.36,
    "endTime": 41.2,
    "text": "they're the co-workers"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.2,
    "endTime": 43.68,
    "text": "who actually keep the engines of our"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.68,
    "endTime": 45.52,
    "text": "organizations running"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.52,
    "endTime": 48.16,
    "text": "but who aren't seen as the innovators"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.16,
    "endTime": 50.8,
    "text": "who drive excellence"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.8,
    "endTime": 52.239,
    "text": "in many ways"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.239,
    "endTime": 54.8,
    "text": "we overlook the folks in the middle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.8,
    "endTime": 57.36,
    "text": "because they don't keep us up awake at"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.36,
    "endTime": 59.44,
    "text": "night wondering what crazy thing they're"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.44,
    "endTime": 62.559,
    "text": "going to come up with next"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.559,
    "endTime": 64.239,
    "text": "and the truth is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.239,
    "endTime": 66.0,
    "text": "that we've come to rely on their"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.0,
    "endTime": 67.68,
    "text": "complacency"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.68,
    "endTime": 70.159,
    "text": "and sense of disconnection"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.159,
    "endTime": 73.92,
    "text": "because it makes our work easier"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.92,
    "endTime": 76.32,
    "text": "you see i know a little bit about the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.32,
    "endTime": 78.4,
    "text": "forgotten middle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.4,
    "endTime": 81.04,
    "text": "as a junior high school student"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.04,
    "endTime": 83.84,
    "text": "i hung out in the middle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.84,
    "endTime": 86.0,
    "text": "for a long time i had been a good"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.0,
    "endTime": 87.2,
    "text": "student"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.2,
    "endTime": 88.799,
    "text": "but seventh grade"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.799,
    "endTime": 90.96,
    "text": "was a game changer"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.96,
    "endTime": 94.0,
    "text": "i spent my days gossiping"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.0,
    "endTime": 95.52,
    "text": "passing notes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.52,
    "endTime": 98.479,
    "text": "generally goofing off with my friends"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.479,
    "endTime": 100.799,
    "text": "i spend my homework time"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.799,
    "endTime": 104.88,
    "text": "on the phone reviewing each day's events"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.88,
    "endTime": 106.72,
    "text": "and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.72,
    "endTime": 109.759,
    "text": "in many ways although i was a typical 12"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.759,
    "endTime": 111.759,
    "text": "year old girl"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.759,
    "endTime": 115.119,
    "text": "my ambivalence about my education"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.119,
    "endTime": 119.04,
    "text": "led to pretty average grades"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.28,
    "endTime": 121.04,
    "text": "luckily for me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.04,
    "endTime": 123.52,
    "text": "my mother understood something"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.52,
    "endTime": 125.04,
    "text": "important"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.04,
    "endTime": 126.64,
    "text": "and that was"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.64,
    "endTime": 128.56,
    "text": "that my location"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.56,
    "endTime": 131.52,
    "text": "was not my destination"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.52,
    "endTime": 132.959,
    "text": "as a former"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.959,
    "endTime": 136.72,
    "text": "research librarian and an educator"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.72,
    "endTime": 139.36,
    "text": "my mother knew that i was capable"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.36,
    "endTime": 143.28,
    "text": "of accomplishing a lot more but she also"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.28,
    "endTime": 144.4,
    "text": "understood"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.4,
    "endTime": 146.56,
    "text": "that because i was a young black woman"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.56,
    "endTime": 147.92,
    "text": "in america"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.92,
    "endTime": 150.56,
    "text": "i might not have opportunities out of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.56,
    "endTime": 153.68,
    "text": "the middle if she wasn't intentional"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.68,
    "endTime": 156.16,
    "text": "about creating them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.16,
    "endTime": 157.36,
    "text": "so"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.36,
    "endTime": 160.239,
    "text": "she moved me to a different school"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.239,
    "endTime": 162.239,
    "text": "she signed me up for leadership"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.239,
    "endTime": 165.12,
    "text": "activities in my neighborhood"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.12,
    "endTime": 167.04,
    "text": "and she began to talk to me more"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.04,
    "endTime": 170.239,
    "text": "seriously about college and career"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.239,
    "endTime": 173.599,
    "text": "options i could aspire to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.599,
    "endTime": 176.16,
    "text": "my mother's formula for getting me out"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.16,
    "endTime": 179.04,
    "text": "of the middle was pretty simple"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.04,
    "endTime": 183.04,
    "text": "she started with high expectations"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.04,
    "endTime": 185.519,
    "text": "she made it her business to figure out"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.519,
    "endTime": 188.879,
    "text": "how to set me up for success"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.879,
    "endTime": 190.72,
    "text": "she held me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.72,
    "endTime": 192.48,
    "text": "accountable"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.48,
    "endTime": 196.319,
    "text": "and along the way she convinced me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.319,
    "endTime": 199.84,
    "text": "that i had the power to create my own"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.84,
    "endTime": 202.239,
    "text": "story"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.239,
    "endTime": 204.72,
    "text": "that formula didn't just help me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.72,
    "endTime": 207.36,
    "text": "get out of my seventh grade slump"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.36,
    "endTime": 210.319,
    "text": "i used it later on in new york city when"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.319,
    "endTime": 212.239,
    "text": "i was working with kids who had a lot of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.239,
    "endTime": 215.519,
    "text": "potential but not a lot of opportunities"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.519,
    "endTime": 218.799,
    "text": "to go to and complete college"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.799,
    "endTime": 221.599,
    "text": "you see high performing students"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.599,
    "endTime": 224.08,
    "text": "tend to have access to additional"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.08,
    "endTime": 226.72,
    "text": "resources like summer enrichment"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.72,
    "endTime": 228.159,
    "text": "activities"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.159,
    "endTime": 231.68,
    "text": "internships and an expansive curriculum"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.68,
    "endTime": 234.4,
    "text": "that takes them out of the classroom and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.4,
    "endTime": 235.76,
    "text": "into the world"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.76,
    "endTime": 237.68,
    "text": "in ways that look great on college"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.68,
    "endTime": 239.599,
    "text": "applications"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.599,
    "endTime": 240.56,
    "text": "but"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.56,
    "endTime": 242.239,
    "text": "we're not providing those kinds of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.239,
    "endTime": 244.56,
    "text": "opportunities for everyone"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244.56,
    "endTime": 247.04,
    "text": "and the result isn't just that some kids"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.04,
    "endTime": 249.84,
    "text": "miss out i think we as a society miss"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.84,
    "endTime": 251.439,
    "text": "out too"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.439,
    "endTime": 254.48,
    "text": "you see i've got a crazy theory about"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.48,
    "endTime": 256.32,
    "text": "the folks in the middle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.32,
    "endTime": 259.28,
    "text": "i think there are some unclaimed winning"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.28,
    "endTime": 261.919,
    "text": "lottery tickets in the middle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.919,
    "endTime": 264.8,
    "text": "i think the cure for cancer and the path"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.8,
    "endTime": 267.68,
    "text": "to world peace might very well reside"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.68,
    "endTime": 269.199,
    "text": "there"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.199,
    "endTime": 270.96,
    "text": "now as a former middle school teacher"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 270.96,
    "endTime": 273.28,
    "text": "i'm not saying that magically everyone"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.28,
    "endTime": 277.12,
    "text": "is suddenly be gonna become an a student"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.12,
    "endTime": 279.04,
    "text": "but i also believe"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.04,
    "endTime": 280.96,
    "text": "that most folks in the middle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.96,
    "endTime": 283.52,
    "text": "are capable of a lot more"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.52,
    "endTime": 285.52,
    "text": "and i think people stay in the middle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285.52,
    "endTime": 287.199,
    "text": "because that's where we've relegated"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287.199,
    "endTime": 289.68,
    "text": "them to and sometimes that's just where"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 289.68,
    "endTime": 291.759,
    "text": "they're kind of chilling while they"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 291.759,
    "endTime": 294.56,
    "text": "figure things out"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 294.56,
    "endTime": 296.479,
    "text": "all of our journeys"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.479,
    "endTime": 299.4,
    "text": "are made up of a series of rest stops"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 299.4,
    "endTime": 301.04,
    "text": "accelerations"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301.04,
    "endTime": 303.68,
    "text": "losses and wins"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 303.68,
    "endTime": 306.4,
    "text": "we have a responsibility to make sure"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306.4,
    "endTime": 308.32,
    "text": "that one's racial"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308.32,
    "endTime": 309.759,
    "text": "gender"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 309.759,
    "endTime": 313.28,
    "text": "cultural and socioeconomic identity"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 313.28,
    "endTime": 315.759,
    "text": "is never the reason you didn't have"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 315.759,
    "endTime": 319.039,
    "text": "access out of the middle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 319.039,
    "endTime": 319.919,
    "text": "so"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 319.919,
    "endTime": 322.16,
    "text": "just as my mother did with me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.16,
    "endTime": 325.36,
    "text": "i began with high expectations with my"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 325.36,
    "endTime": 326.72,
    "text": "young people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 326.72,
    "endTime": 328.88,
    "text": "and i started with the question"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.88,
    "endTime": 331.12,
    "text": "i stopped asking kids"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 331.12,
    "endTime": 333.36,
    "text": "hey do you want to go to college"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 333.36,
    "endTime": 335.44,
    "text": "i started asking them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 335.44,
    "endTime": 338.72,
    "text": "what college would you like to attend"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 338.72,
    "endTime": 342.16,
    "text": "you see the first question"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 345.52,
    "endTime": 347.199,
    "text": "the first question"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 347.199,
    "endTime": 350.479,
    "text": "leaves a lot of vague possibilities open"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 350.479,
    "endTime": 352.479,
    "text": "but the second question"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 352.479,
    "endTime": 354.96,
    "text": "says something about what i thought my"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 354.96,
    "endTime": 357.6,
    "text": "young people were capable of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 357.6,
    "endTime": 359.759,
    "text": "on a basic level it assumes that they're"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 359.759,
    "endTime": 362.0,
    "text": "going to graduate from high school"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 362.0,
    "endTime": 363.6,
    "text": "successfully"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 363.6,
    "endTime": 366.639,
    "text": "it also assumed that they would have the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 366.639,
    "endTime": 369.6,
    "text": "kinds of academic records that could get"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 369.6,
    "endTime": 373.6,
    "text": "them college and university admissions"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 373.6,
    "endTime": 374.639,
    "text": "and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 374.639,
    "endTime": 376.0,
    "text": "i'm proud to say that the high"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 376.0,
    "endTime": 377.919,
    "text": "expectations worked"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 377.919,
    "endTime": 380.479,
    "text": "while black and latinx students"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 380.479,
    "endTime": 383.199,
    "text": "nationally tend to graduate from college"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 383.199,
    "endTime": 385.039,
    "text": "in six years or less"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 385.039,
    "endTime": 388.16,
    "text": "at a percent of 38"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 388.16,
    "endTime": 390.96,
    "text": "we were recognized by the college board"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 390.96,
    "endTime": 393.36,
    "text": "for our ability not to just get kids"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 393.36,
    "endTime": 395.6,
    "text": "into college but to get them through"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 395.6,
    "endTime": 398.08,
    "text": "college"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 403.199,
    "endTime": 405.52,
    "text": "but i also understand that high"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 405.52,
    "endTime": 407.68,
    "text": "expectations are great but it takes a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 407.68,
    "endTime": 409.52,
    "text": "little bit more than that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 409.52,
    "endTime": 412.24,
    "text": "you wouldn't ask a pastry chef to bake a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 412.24,
    "endTime": 414.16,
    "text": "cake without an oven"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 414.16,
    "endTime": 416.479,
    "text": "and we should not be asking the folks in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 416.479,
    "endTime": 417.44,
    "text": "the middle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 417.44,
    "endTime": 419.919,
    "text": "to make the leap without providing them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 419.919,
    "endTime": 421.36,
    "text": "with the tools"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 421.36,
    "endTime": 425.039,
    "text": "strategies and support they deserve to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 425.039,
    "endTime": 428.24,
    "text": "make progress in their lives"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 428.24,
    "endTime": 430.56,
    "text": "a young woman i had been mentoring for a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 430.56,
    "endTime": 431.759,
    "text": "long time"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 431.759,
    "endTime": 435.12,
    "text": "nicole came to my office one day after"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 435.12,
    "endTime": 438.0,
    "text": "her guidance counselor looked at her"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 438.0,
    "endTime": 440.88,
    "text": "pretty strong transcript and expressed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 440.88,
    "endTime": 443.36,
    "text": "utter shock and amazement that she was"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 443.36,
    "endTime": 446.88,
    "text": "even interested in going to college"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 446.88,
    "endTime": 449.599,
    "text": "what the guidance counselor didn't know"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 449.599,
    "endTime": 452.319,
    "text": "was that through her community nicole"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 452.319,
    "endTime": 455.52,
    "text": "had had access to college prep work"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 455.52,
    "endTime": 458.56,
    "text": "s.a.t prep and international travel"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 458.56,
    "endTime": 460.16,
    "text": "programs"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 460.16,
    "endTime": 463.12,
    "text": "not only was college in her future"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 463.12,
    "endTime": 465.199,
    "text": "but i'm proud to say that nicole went on"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 465.199,
    "endTime": 466.24,
    "text": "to earn"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 466.24,
    "endTime": 469.039,
    "text": "two master's degrees after graduating"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 469.039,
    "endTime": 471.62,
    "text": "from purdue university"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 471.62,
    "endTime": 474.819,
    "text": "[Applause]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 477.039,
    "endTime": 479.36,
    "text": "we also made it our business"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 479.36,
    "endTime": 482.08,
    "text": "to hold our young people accountable"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 482.08,
    "endTime": 484.479,
    "text": "but also to instill a sense of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 484.479,
    "endTime": 486.08,
    "text": "accountability"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 486.08,
    "endTime": 489.199,
    "text": "in those young people to themselves"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 489.199,
    "endTime": 492.16,
    "text": "to each other to their families and to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 492.16,
    "endTime": 494.0,
    "text": "their communities"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 494.0,
    "endTime": 497.199,
    "text": "we doubled down on asset based youth"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 497.199,
    "endTime": 498.56,
    "text": "development"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 498.56,
    "endTime": 501.12,
    "text": "we went on leadership retreats and did"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 501.12,
    "endTime": 504.479,
    "text": "high ropes courses and low ropes courses"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 504.479,
    "endTime": 507.84,
    "text": "and tackled life's biggest questions"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 507.84,
    "endTime": 509.44,
    "text": "together"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 509.44,
    "endTime": 511.44,
    "text": "the result was that the kids really"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 511.44,
    "endTime": 513.919,
    "text": "bought into the notion that they were"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 513.919,
    "endTime": 515.279,
    "text": "accountable"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 515.279,
    "endTime": 518.56,
    "text": "for achieving these college degrees"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 518.56,
    "endTime": 521.44,
    "text": "it was so gratifying to see the kids"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 521.44,
    "endTime": 523.919,
    "text": "calling each other and texting each"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 523.919,
    "endTime": 526.64,
    "text": "other to say hey why are you late for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 526.64,
    "endTime": 528.08,
    "text": "s.a.t prep"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 528.08,
    "endTime": 530.399,
    "text": "and what are you packing for the college"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 530.399,
    "endTime": 532.959,
    "text": "tour tomorrow"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 532.959,
    "endTime": 535.279,
    "text": "we really worked to kind of make college"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 535.279,
    "endTime": 537.6,
    "text": "the thing to do"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 537.6,
    "endTime": 541.04,
    "text": "we began to create programs on college"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 541.04,
    "endTime": 542.24,
    "text": "campuses"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 542.24,
    "endTime": 545.2,
    "text": "and events that allowed young people to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 545.2,
    "endTime": 548.08,
    "text": "really visualize themselves as college"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 548.08,
    "endTime": 551.04,
    "text": "students and college graduates"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 551.04,
    "endTime": 553.6,
    "text": "me and my staff rocked our own college"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 553.6,
    "endTime": 556.08,
    "text": "gear and had lots of fun healthy"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 556.08,
    "endTime": 559.04,
    "text": "competition about whose school was"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 559.04,
    "endTime": 561.2,
    "text": "better than whose"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 561.2,
    "endTime": 563.6,
    "text": "the kids really bought into it and they"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 563.6,
    "endTime": 566.32,
    "text": "began to see that something more was"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 566.32,
    "endTime": 568.8,
    "text": "possible for their lives"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 568.8,
    "endTime": 571.279,
    "text": "not only that they could look around at"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 571.279,
    "endTime": 573.68,
    "text": "that college-going community and see"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 573.68,
    "endTime": 576.24,
    "text": "kids who came from the same backgrounds"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 576.24,
    "endTime": 578.48,
    "text": "and the same neighborhoods and who were"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 578.48,
    "endTime": 581.92,
    "text": "aspiring to the same things"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 581.92,
    "endTime": 585.519,
    "text": "that sense of belonging was really key"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 585.519,
    "endTime": 587.68,
    "text": "and it showed up in a remarkable"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 587.68,
    "endTime": 590.16,
    "text": "beautiful way one day when we were in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 590.16,
    "endTime": 593.279,
    "text": "the johannesburg airport waiting to go"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 593.279,
    "endTime": 595.68,
    "text": "through customs on our way to botswana"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 595.68,
    "endTime": 597.92,
    "text": "for a service learning trip"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 597.92,
    "endTime": 599.92,
    "text": "i saw a group of kids kind of huddled in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 599.92,
    "endTime": 601.68,
    "text": "a circle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 601.68,
    "endTime": 603.12,
    "text": "usually with teens that means"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 603.12,
    "endTime": 605.92,
    "text": "something's going on"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 606.24,
    "endTime": 608.56,
    "text": "so i kind of walked up behind the kids"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 608.56,
    "endTime": 610.32,
    "text": "to figure out what they were talking"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 610.32,
    "endTime": 611.68,
    "text": "about"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 611.68,
    "endTime": 615.279,
    "text": "they were comparing passport stamps"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 615.279,
    "endTime": 617.6,
    "text": "and they were dreaming out loud about"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 617.6,
    "endTime": 620.399,
    "text": "all the other countries they plan to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 620.399,
    "endTime": 622.64,
    "text": "visit in the future"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 622.64,
    "endTime": 624.24,
    "text": "and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 624.24,
    "endTime": 626.16,
    "text": "seeing these young people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 626.16,
    "endTime": 628.959,
    "text": "from new york city go on to not just"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 628.959,
    "endTime": 631.2,
    "text": "become college students but to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 631.2,
    "endTime": 634.16,
    "text": "participate in study abroad programs and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 634.16,
    "endTime": 637.2,
    "text": "to then take jobs around the world was"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 637.2,
    "endTime": 639.6,
    "text": "incredibly gratifying"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 639.6,
    "endTime": 641.92,
    "text": "when i think of my kids and all the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 641.92,
    "endTime": 643.92,
    "text": "doctors lawyers"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 643.92,
    "endTime": 647.12,
    "text": "teachers social workers journalists and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 647.12,
    "endTime": 650.48,
    "text": "artists who came from our little nook in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 650.48,
    "endTime": 652.079,
    "text": "new york city"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 652.079,
    "endTime": 654.079,
    "text": "i hate to think of what would have"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 654.079,
    "endTime": 656.88,
    "text": "happened if we hadn't invested in the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 656.88,
    "endTime": 658.0,
    "text": "middle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 658.0,
    "endTime": 659.68,
    "text": "just think about all that their"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 659.68,
    "endTime": 662.0,
    "text": "communities and the world would have"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 662.0,
    "endTime": 664.56,
    "text": "missed out on"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 664.56,
    "endTime": 667.519,
    "text": "this formula for the middle doesn't just"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 667.519,
    "endTime": 669.6,
    "text": "work with young people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 669.6,
    "endTime": 672.24,
    "text": "it can transform our organizations as"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 672.24,
    "endTime": 673.76,
    "text": "well"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 673.76,
    "endTime": 676.959,
    "text": "we can be more bold and coming up and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 676.959,
    "endTime": 679.839,
    "text": "articulating a mission that inspires"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 679.839,
    "endTime": 681.36,
    "text": "everyone"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 681.36,
    "endTime": 683.68,
    "text": "we can authentically invite our"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 683.68,
    "endTime": 686.48,
    "text": "colleagues to the table to come up with"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 686.48,
    "endTime": 690.0,
    "text": "a strategy to meet the mission"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 690.0,
    "endTime": 693.12,
    "text": "we can give meaningful feedback to folks"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 693.12,
    "endTime": 695.12,
    "text": "along the way"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 695.12,
    "endTime": 698.399,
    "text": "and and sometimes most importantly"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 698.399,
    "endTime": 701.2,
    "text": "make sure that you're sharing credit for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 701.2,
    "endTime": 704.959,
    "text": "everyone's contributions"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 705.12,
    "endTime": 708.0,
    "text": "what happened when my staff aimed high"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 708.0,
    "endTime": 709.68,
    "text": "for themselves"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 709.68,
    "endTime": 711.76,
    "text": "is that what they were able to do for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 711.76,
    "endTime": 715.6,
    "text": "young people was pretty transformational"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 715.6,
    "endTime": 718.48,
    "text": "and it's been so wonderful to look back"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 718.48,
    "endTime": 720.72,
    "text": "and see all of my former colleagues"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 720.72,
    "endTime": 723.12,
    "text": "who've gone on to get doctorates and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 723.12,
    "endTime": 725.68,
    "text": "assume leadership roles in other"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 725.68,
    "endTime": 728.48,
    "text": "organizations"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 728.48,
    "endTime": 730.48,
    "text": "we have what it takes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 730.48,
    "endTime": 732.0,
    "text": "to inspire"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 732.0,
    "endTime": 735.36,
    "text": "and uplift the folks in the middle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 735.36,
    "endTime": 738.959,
    "text": "we can extend love to the people in the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 738.959,
    "endTime": 740.16,
    "text": "middle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 740.16,
    "endTime": 743.279,
    "text": "we can challenge our own biases about"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 743.279,
    "endTime": 747.839,
    "text": "who deserves a hand up and how"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 747.839,
    "endTime": 750.72,
    "text": "we can structure our organizations"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 750.72,
    "endTime": 753.519,
    "text": "communities and institutions in ways"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 753.519,
    "endTime": 756.0,
    "text": "that are inclusive and that uphold"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 756.0,
    "endTime": 758.639,
    "text": "principles of equity"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 758.639,
    "endTime": 761.519,
    "text": "because in the final analysis"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 761.519,
    "endTime": 765.2,
    "text": "what is often mistaken for a period"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 765.2,
    "endTime": 766.399,
    "text": "is really"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 766.399,
    "endTime": 768.32,
    "text": "just a comma"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 768.32,
    "endTime": 771.56,
    "text": "thank you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 778.16,
    "endTime": 780.24,
    "text": "you"
  }
]